					This friendly message is coming from:
					<ul>
						<li>Your controller at
							<code>
								<a href="{{ '/home/vgillet/Symfony-initialized/base_project_bootstrap/src/Controller/HomeController.php'|file_link(0) }}">src/Controller/HomeController.php</a>
